data.description: Ready to buy down your rate?? The sellers are willing to give you $8000 in closing costs to do just that! Built-in 2018, this stunning has 4 bedrooms & 2 baths. The 4th bedroom can also be used as an office. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a cozy night with your loved ones. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, plenty of granite counter space, and a kitchen pantry. The primary bedroom features a large walk-in closet &a lovely ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub and separate fully tiled shower. The secondary bedrooms offer good space and storage. The office area located at the front of the home offers tons of natural light and privacy so you can work in peace. Outside, you'll find a covered back patio and yard that is perfect for hosting BBQs. Located just minutes away from local schools, shops, restaurants and a brand new movie theater. Come see what this beautiful home has to offer.
